    <div class="titles">

        <h1>Photo of the year, eMTBs, and MvdP interested in enduro: Pinkbike Digest</h1>

		            <p class="author">by Sarah Lukas</p>
		
        <div class="meta">

			                <p class="date">February 25, 2020</p>
			
			
	        
			
        </div>

